    {
      "id": "PopularPost348953",
      "post_content": "[Serra Avatar](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Serra Avatar), [Rhox Faithmender](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rhox Faithmender), [Boon Reflection](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boon Reflection). \"At the beginning of your end step, quintuple your life total.\"  \n  \n@KingSupernova: Not quite. Let's say you have 40 life. At the beginning of your end step, you gain 40 from Serra Avatar. Faithmender doubles it to 80, and Reflection doubles that to 160, so you end up with 200 life.",
      "posted_by": "Continue",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost348953\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\"><a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Serra Avatar\">Serra Avatar</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rhox Faithmender\">Rhox Faithmender</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boon Reflection\">Boon Reflection</a>. \"At the beginning of your end step, quintuple your life total.\"<br/><br/>@KingSupernova: Not quite. Let's say you have 40 life. At the beginning of your end step, you gain 40 from Serra Avatar. Faithmender doubles it to 80, and Reflection doubles that to 160, so you end up with 200 life.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy88902\">Continue</span>\r\n                                (4/6/2014 6:07:45 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightC